hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Where are you calling from? where to buy prostacet Obama is a lemon. Michelle is... what, some kind of counterpart lemon? I don't want the US to attack Syria. I don't want my kids to have to eat tofu as their school lunch. I just want them both to go far, FAR away. Perhaps next time we can actually find a candidate who will DELIVER on some hope and change, like NO MORE WARS OF AGGRESSION for starters. And then there's the NSA spying thing... Not a good time to be appearing in public, Michelle, the villagers are angry. Perhaps another vacation? Have fun! Stay gone!
